OL,3,CHusband accused of drugging wife for
OL,4,Cmen to abuse admits rape and sexual
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FAdditional reporting by ITV Senior
OL,8,FProducers Eleanor Gregory and Louisa
OL,9,FFelton
OL,11,FA man accused of drugging his wife for
OL,12,Fhimself and multiple other men to
OL,13,Fsexually abuse has today admitted
OL,14,Fseveral sexual offences against her,
OL,15,Fincluding rape and sexual assault.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
