OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782211684
OL,3,CHusband accused of drugging wife for
OL,4,Cmen to abuse admits rape and sexual
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FThe husband, who cannot be named for
OL,8,Flegal reasons, pleaded guilty at
OL,9,FManchester's Minshull Street Crown
OL,10,FCourt on Monday to raping and sexually
OL,11,Fassaulting his wife over three years
OL,12,Fbetween 2022 and 2025.
OL,14,FHe also admitted to sharing intimate
OL,15,Fimages and films of her without her
OL,16,Fconsent for sexual gratification.
OL,18,FHe had previously denied all 48
OL,19,Fcharges against him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
