PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782211684
OL,3,CHusband accused of drugging wife for
OL,4,Cmen to abuse admits rape and sexual
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FHe still faces trial on 1 September
OL,8,Fover the remaining allegations,
OL,9,Fincluding conspiracy to rape and
OL,10,Fconspiracy to administer a substance
OL,11,Fwith intent to stupefy or overpower.
OL,13,FThese allegations, namely that he
OL,14,Fdrugged his wife, span twenty years,
OL,15,Fdating back to 2004.
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
