OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782211684
OL,3,CHusband accused of drugging wife for
OL,4,Cmen to abuse admits rape and sexual
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FOn Monday, the man was formally called
OL,8,Fto court on several allegations and
OL,9,Fspoke softly as he entered his new
OL,10,Fpleas.
OL,12,FTwelve other defendants, who also
OL,13,Fcannot be named for legal reasons,
OL,14,Fwill stand trial alongside the husband
OL,15,Fand face similar charges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
