OL,7,FA thirteenth defendant, a man in his
OL,8,Ffifties from Scotland, has already
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to four offences,
OL,10,Fincluding conspiracy to rape and
OL,11,Fconspiracy to administer a substance
OL,12,Fwith intent to stupefy or overpower a
OL,13,Fperson.
OL,15,FIf you, or someone you know, has been
OL,16,Fa victim of rape of sexual violence,
OL,17,Fthere is support out there to help:
